<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 text-black dark:text-white p-3 md:p-6 transition-colors duration-300"
     data-controller="exercise-checker text-toggle font-controls"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <!-- Info Box -->
  <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 p-4 md:p-6 pb-8 rounded-lg">
    <div class="space-y-4 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="font-semibold text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 mb-2"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Quando il soggetto compie l'azione, il verbo è usato nella <strong>forma attiva</strong>:</p>
        <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30 rounded p-3 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-2 text-center">
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">soggetto</p>
              <p class="font-bold">Eva</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">verbo (forma attiva)</p>
              <p class="font-bold">legge</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">compl. oggetto</p>
              <p class="font-bold">un libro</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="font-semibold text-green-700 dark:text-green-400 mb-2"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Quando il soggetto subisce l'azione, il verbo è usato nella <strong>forma passiva</strong>:</p>
        <div class="bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/30 rounded p-3 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-2 text-center">
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">soggetto</p>
              <p class="font-bold">Il libro</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">verbo (forma passiva)</p>
              <p class="font-bold">è letto</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">compl. indiretto</p>
              <p class="font-bold">da Eva</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <ul class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 pl-4">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400 font-bold">•</span>
          <span>Nella forma passiva i verbi sono accompagnati dall'ausiliare <strong>essere</strong> o da <strong>venire</strong> → <em>è letto, viene letto</em>.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-bold">•</span>
          <span>I verbi transitivi possono avere sia la forma attiva sia quella passiva → <em>Eva legge il libro. / Il libro è letto da Eva</em>.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 font-bold">•</span>
          <span>I verbi intransitivi possono avere solo la forma attiva → <em>Luca cammina</em>.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 1: IMPARARE TUTTI -->
  <div class="p-4 md:p-6 pb-8" data-controller="multiple-choice">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">1</span>
      Sottolinea i verbi e per ciascuno scrivi se è di forma attiva (FA) o di forma passiva (FP).
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
      <% sentences = [
        { text: "L'olmo <mark class=\"bg-yellow-200 dark:bg-yellow-600/50 dark:text-white\">è stato colpito</mark> da un fulmine.", correct: "FP" },
        { text: "<mark class=\"bg-yellow-200 dark:bg-yellow-600/50 dark:text-white\">Hai innaffiato</mark> troppo l'orchidea.", correct: "FA" },
        { text: "Il nonno <mark class=\"bg-yellow-200 dark:bg-yellow-600/50 dark:text-white\">fu assunto</mark> dall'azienda.", correct: "FP" },
        { text: "La città <mark class=\"bg-yellow-200 dark:bg-yellow-600/50 dark:text-white\">è stata ricostruita</mark> completamente.", correct: "FP" },
        { text: "Il polline <mark class=\"bg-yellow-200 dark:bg-yellow-600/50 dark:text-white\">viene trasportato</mark> dal vento.", correct: "FP" },
        { text: "Io e Isa <mark class=\"bg-yellow-200 dark:bg-yellow-600/50 dark:text-white\">frequenteremo</mark> la prima media.", correct: "FA" },
        { text: "La mamma <mark class=\"bg-yellow-200 dark:bg-yellow-600/50 dark:text-white\">è stata nominata</mark> direttrice.", correct: "FP" },
        { text: "Paolo <mark class=\"bg-yellow-200 dark:bg-yellow-600/50 dark:text-white\">scrisse</mark> molte poesie.", correct: "FA" },
        { text: "La canzone vincitrice <mark class=\"bg-yellow-200 dark:bg-yellow-600/50 dark:text-white\">sarà proclamata</mark> domani dalla giuria.", correct: "FP" },
        { text: "L'attore <mark class=\"bg-yellow-200 dark:bg-yellow-600/50 dark:text-white\">riceve</mark> l'applauso del pubblico.", correct: "FA" }
      ] %>

      <% sentences.each_with_index do |item, idx| %>
        <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-3 flex items-center justify-between">
          <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <%= item[:text].html_safe %></span>
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_<%= idx + 1 %>" value="FA" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">FA</span></label>
            <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><input type="radio" name="ex1_<%= idx + 1 %>" value="FP" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">FP</span></label>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="text-right text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">
    Esercizi p. <%= link_to "172", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p172"), class: "text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-800 dark:hover:text-gray-200 underline" %>
  </div>

  <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
</div>
